Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.53,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない　でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.53,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛 or 盾？ 不想认输 可是又不愿受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って　確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.52,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑一样在手中仔细掂量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.72,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.72,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是发现再要反悔为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:35.17,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:35.17,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选的是哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.95,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.47,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.47,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  温柔是弱点
