Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开枪 约拿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶..那个臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅！不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要灭了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clear
